---
const objectives = [
    "Build an AI system around one person's actual needs.",
    'Use AI deeply without giving up ownership.',
    'Start from a seed that can become fully your own.',
    'Do serious work in a way that still feels playful and satisfying.',
];
---

<div class="grid gap-10">
    <section class="grid gap-8">
        <figure
            class="relative grid justify-items-center gap-5 overflow-hidden rounded-[1.35rem_0.95rem_1.15rem_0.92rem] border border-stone-400/14 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.5),rgba(251,247,241,0.52)),repeating-linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(120,113,108,0.038)_0,rgba(120,113,108,0.038)_1px,transparent_1px,transparent_33px)] px-6 py-10 text-center shadow-[0_10px_28px_rgba(43,36,29,0.04),inset_0_1px_0_rgba(255,255,255,0.62)] md:px-10 md:py-14"
        >
            <span
                aria-hidden="true"
                class="pointer-events-none absolute -top-12 -right-12 h-44 w-44 rounded-full bg-[radial-gradient(circle,rgba(21,74,122,0.1),transparent_72%)]"
            ></span>
            <span
                aria-hidden="true"
                class="pointer-events-none absolute -bottom-16 -left-12 h-48 w-48 rounded-full bg-[radial-gradient(circle,rgba(180,83,9,0.08),transparent_70%)]"
            ></span>

            <p
                class="m-0 font-['IBM_Plex_Mono',monospace] text-[0.6rem] tracking-[0.22em] text-[#154a7a] uppercase"
            >
                In one line
            </p>

            <blockquote class="m-0 w-full">
                <p
                    class="m-0 text-[clamp(2.2rem,3.8vw,3rem)] leading-none text-[#2b241d] [text-wrap:balance]"
                    style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;"
                >
                    GalexC is Professional-Grade Personal AI
                </p>
            </blockquote>

            <span
                aria-hidden="true"
                class="block h-px w-32 bg-[rgba(21,74,122,0.3)]"></span>
        </figure>

        <div class="grid gap-4 border-t border-stone-400/14 pt-6">
            <div
                class="flex max-w-[46rem] items-end justify-between gap-3 border-b border-stone-400/12 pb-2.5"
            >
                <p class="eyebrow">Objectives</p>
            </div>

            <ol class="m-0 grid list-none gap-3 p-0 sm:grid-cols-2">
                {
                    objectives.map((objective, index) => (
                        <li class="group relative grid gap-3 rounded-2xl border border-stone-400/14 bg-white/40 p-5 shadow-[inset_0_1px_0_rgba(255,255,255,0.55)] transition-[transform,border-color,box-shadow] duration-300 ease-[cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1)] hover:-translate-y-px hover:border-[rgba(21,74,122,0.2)] hover:shadow-[0_14px_30px_rgba(43,36,29,0.06),inset_0_1px_0_rgba(255,255,255,0.6)]">
                            <header class="flex items-baseline justify-between gap-2">
                                <span class="font-['IBM_Plex_Mono',monospace] text-[0.68rem] tracking-[0.18em] text-[#7a6d60] uppercase">
                                    {String(index + 1).padStart(2, '0')}
                                </span>
                                <span
                                    aria-hidden="true"
                                    class="block h-px w-10 bg-[rgba(120,113,108,0.22)] transition-colors duration-300 group-hover:bg-[rgba(21,74,122,0.32)]"
                                />
                            </header>
                            <p class="m-0 leading-relaxed text-[#4f4438]">
                                {objective}
                            </p>
                        </li>
                    ))
                }
            </ol>
        </div>

        <aside
            class="grid max-w-[46rem] gap-2 border-l-2 border-l-[rgba(21,74,122,0.18)] pl-5"
        >
            <p
                class="m-0 font-['IBM_Plex_Mono',monospace] text-[0.6rem] tracking-[0.18em] text-[#154a7a] uppercase"
            >
                Why bother
            </p>
            <p class="m-0 text-base leading-[1.8] text-[#564a3f]">
                If GalexC achieves its objectives, it could make room for better
                work, better decisions, and a better way of moving through the
                digital world. If it never becomes more than what it is today, a
                personal project that has been genuinely, deeply fun to build, I
                count this as a success.
            </p>
        </aside>

        <div
            class="grid grid-cols-1 overflow-hidden rounded-[1.35rem_0.95rem_1.15rem_0.92rem] border border-stone-400/14 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.46),rgba(251,247,241,0.42))] shadow-[0_10px_28px_rgba(43,36,29,0.04),inset_0_1px_0_rgba(255,255,255,0.6)] sm:grid-cols-2"
        >
            <div
                class="grid gap-2 p-6 sm:border-r sm:border-stone-400/14 md:p-8"
            >
                <span
                    class="font-['IBM_Plex_Mono',monospace] text-[0.6rem] tracking-[0.22em] text-[#7a6d60] uppercase"
                >
                    01 / Posture
                </span>
                <p
                    class="m-0 text-[clamp(1.6rem,3.2vw,2.4rem)] leading-none whitespace-nowrap text-[#2b241d]"
                    style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;"
                >
                    Personal first.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div
                class="grid gap-2 border-t border-stone-400/14 p-6 sm:border-t-0 md:p-8"
            >
                <span
                    class="font-['IBM_Plex_Mono',monospace] text-[0.6rem] tracking-[0.22em] text-[#154a7a] uppercase"
                >
                    02 / Standard
                </span>
                <p
                    class="m-0 text-[clamp(1.6rem,3.2vw,2.4rem)] leading-none whitespace-nowrap text-[#2b241d]"
                    style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;"
                >
                    Professional grade.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>
